              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "ThO2 powder of 99.7% purity were pressed into",
                "circular disks with a diameter of 14 mm. The",
                "thickness of sample was about 2 mm. Each sample was",
                "sandwiched between two monitor aluminum (thin Al foil",
                "of 99.99% purity)foils."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Irradiation of the samples was lasted about",
                "117 minutes with the neutrons flux yield about 2 E11",
                "n/(4pi*s). The samples were placed at 0, 45, 90 degree",
                "angles relative to the deuterium beam direction and",
                "centered about the T-Ti target at a distance of 35 mm."
              ]
            }
          ],
